HEADWORD: Marlstone
<hw>Marl"stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>
<def>A sandy calcareous stratum, containing, or impregnated with, iron,
and lying between the upper and lower Lias of England.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

